title: Central AC
des: A central air conditioner is a type of a ir conditioning system that cools and dehumidifies the air in a home or building. It consists of an indoor unit and an outdoor unit connected by refrigerant lines.

title: Ductless/Mini-Split AC
des: ductless or mini-split air conditioner is a type of air conditioning system that does not require ducts to distribute cooled air throughout a home or building

title: Floor Mounted
des: Floor mounted air conditioning units are a type of air conditioning system that is installed on the floor of a room or space.
